{"word":"λῃστής","slug":"λῃστής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λῃστής</b></el> <el>(λῃστής, οῦ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ληίζομαι'><el>ληίζομαι</el></a>\n<p/><i>a robber, plunderer</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> by sea, <i>a pirate, rover, buccaneer</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}